room_title: Escape room "School of Magic" by The Cube Escape Rooms in Santa Barbara
room_description:
A dark force has taken over the last School of Magic.
The teachers have succumb to it’s power. If the school is not saved, the dark force will take over the world.
You are the only wizards left unknown to the dark force’s knowledge. You must create the magic potion to lift the black Magic’s veil of power and save the world as we know it.
